{"title":"<h2>Why Another Heckin' Website?</h2>","weight":"2","content":"\u003cp\u003eThis site seeks to model a text heavy informative website (like a manual or textbook) while also utilizing many of the current available \u003cabbr title='HyperText Markup Language'\u003eHTML\u003c/abbr\u003e elements. We\u0026rsquo;ll also create a small but sensible set of styling instructions in \u003cabbr title='Cascading Style Sheets'\u003eCSS\u003c/abbr\u003e and a couple of handy but optional \u003cabbr title='Javascript'\u003eJS\u003c/abbr\u003e features.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \n\n    \u003caside\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eLearning web design?\u003c/h3\u003e\n    \n        \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \u003csource srcset='https://philotfarnsworth.github.io/APrettyHuGOinWebsite/diatribes/why/images/dunceMobile.avif' type='image/avif' media='(max-width: 800px)' /\u003e\n        \u003csource srcset='https://philotfarnsworth.github.io/APrettyHuGOinWebsite/diatribes/why/images/dunceMobile.webp' type='image/webp' media='(max-width: 800px)' /\u003e\n        \u003csource srcset='https://philotfarnsworth.github.io/APrettyHuGOinWebsite/diatribes/why/images/dunceMobile.png' media='(max-width: 800px)' /\u003e\n        \u003csource srcset='https://philotfarnsworth.github.io/APrettyHuGOinWebsite/diatribes/why/images/dunce.avif' type='image/avif' /\u003e\n        \u003csource srcset='https://philotfarnsworth.github.io/APrettyHuGOinWebsite/diatribes/why/images/dunce.webp' type='image/webp' /\u003e\n        \u003cimg src='https://philotfarnsworth.github.io/APrettyHuGOinWebsite/diatribes/why/images/dunce.png' alt='Armored man dons a pointy dunce cap.' /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \n\u003c/figure\u003e\n    \n    \u003cp\u003eGet ready to be schooled!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/aside\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n         By doing so across both Single Page Application (\u003cabbr\u003eSPA\u003c/abbr\u003e) and static experiences, we ensure our content is 